Explain a diagnostic code

Usage: elp explain [OPTIONS] --code <CODE>

Options:
      --code <CODE>  Error code to explain
  -h, --help         Print help

Global options:
      --log-file <LOG_FILE>  
      --erl <ERL>            
      --escript <ESCRIPT>    
      --no-log-buffering     
      --no-buck-generated    When using buck, do not invoke a build step for generated files
      --buck-quick-start     Use buck2 targets for first stage project loading
      --ifdef                Enable ifdef/ifndef condition evaluation (experimental)
      --color <WHEN>         Use color in output [default: always] [possible values: always, never,
                             auto]
